.edit-profile-bio-input:focus{
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent-amber);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.12);
}
```
**Rationale:** These exactly mirror `.auth-input` from signup.css (lines 214-244) -- same border, background, focus glow with gold accent, placeholder styling.

**Replace `.input-title-container`** (line 246-251):
```css
.input-title-container{
