        ? "input-title username-status-checking" 
        : usernameAvailable === true 
            ? "input-title username-status-available" 
            : usernameAvailable === false 
                ? "input-title username-status-taken" 
                : "input-title"
}>
    {usernameChecking ? 'Checking...' : usernameAvailable === true ? '\u2713 Available' : usernameAvailable === false ? '\u2717 Taken' : ''}
</span>
```
**Rationale:** Uses Unicode checkmark and X characters for immediate visual feedback. Green for available (uses `--color-success`, same as the form success message on signup), red for taken (uses `--color-danger`). No new SVG icons needed -- keeps it simple.

